ctime=time.sel(time=slice('1960','2016'))
xtime=ctime.isel(time=np.arange(1,57*12-1)).values

nstep=int(57*12-2)
index=np.zeros(nstep)
ul=np.zeros(nstep)
dl=np.zeros(nstep)
for i in range(0,nstep):
    index[i]=np.mean(ds_anom[i:i+3])
    ul[i]=0.5
    dl[i]=-0.5

plt.xlabel('year')
plt.plot(xtime,index)
plt.plot(xtime,ul,'r')
plt.plot(xtime,dl,'b')
plt.show()

High_Cloud_Area = Cloud_Mean.where(Cloud_Mean >= 75.0)

High_Cloud_SW = TOA_SW_Mean * (High_Cloud_Area / High_Cloud_Area)
